{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1087810/extras/HeaderGif.gif?t=1699039158\" /><br><br><strong>In Forgetful Dictator, knowledge is power!</strong> Conquer countries by simply learning their names. Answer trivia questions, survive time trials, identify national flags and capitals. Can you defeat the dictator's oldest enemy, the tyrannosaurus tyrant? And his true nemesis, forgetfulness?<br><br>Forgetful Dictator is a hilarious <strong>geography game with strategy elements</strong>, somehow suitable for all ages. It\u2019s the weirdest way to teach yourself about the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Conquer the world:</strong> 180+ countries and territories to learn and conquer. <br></li><li><strong>Triumph over trivia</strong>: hundreds of carefully selected trivia questions to answer, chosen for their useful or surprising facts. Less \u201c3rd highest mountain in Asia\u201d, and more \u201cWhich countries have nuclear weapons?\u201d<br></li><li><strong>Defeat the Dino Dictator</strong>: the dino can conquer countries, forcing you to answer specific trivia questions about them. But he\u2019s a very nice and deserving person, best just to let him have it. <br></li><li><strong>Get strategic</strong>: acquire hints from answering trivia questions, and use them to help name the countries. Don\u2019t run out of armies or you\u2019ll meet the firing squad\u2026and get fired!<br></li><li><strong>Manage upgrades</strong>: on your quest for world domination you will acquire bonuses, complete missions, launch BlitzCraigs, and even fire superweapons (gently).  <br></li><li><strong>Have a hearty chortle</strong>: with hundreds of hilarious dialogue lines, you can laugh while you learn! Every character is a different flavour of dork.   <br></li><li><strong>Unlock rewards</strong>: including different unlockable gamemodes, with modes that focus on flags and capitals.<br></li><li><strong>Challenge yourself</strong>: with achievements and hardcore options. Can you become a master of <i>basic geography</i>?</li></ul><br>This is a free game with no ads or microtransactions. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1087810/extras/GameplayFast.gif?t=1699039158\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Flags in the Bag","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/526b613ac2649de9cd454a008bef37c6a2c0d967.jpg"},{"name":"Vexillology","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/941b0ce171c63f46f0e19842b57e70554523eb43.jpg"},{"name":"Capital Captain","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/0a5602e5ea460958e56f5d971f84f85e503fda67.jpg"},{"name":"Admiral Capital","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/ee52458b41a09c9d7ddd829af5a65085f6d88598.jpg"},{"name":"Lightning Score","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/fb0c36a7f8bd44057dc97762129bd55c79c7cff6.jpg"},{"name":"Sweaty Palms","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/1dbc4d33fc5313e4b07a49fe7e2ca666a820e833.jpg"},{"name":"Land Down Under","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/d976f7362bc32a7f1b85a9fe192d6afe0f140095.jpg"},{"name":"How It Was Meant To Be","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/f4de5447fcfe5e6782242e5083de6066ba6e7c1c.jpg"},{"name":"Victory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/db29713bf89824629c5984e00d5a99e4cfb20ca3.jpg"},{"name":"Sweet Victory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1087810/7dbd7a1e8e900f49b82ba639b513fb6db583cf03.jpg"}],"total":20},"background":"ht